{"tid":921660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[大怒] 有人送100萬現金比娛樂台女神張元英 元英BB","createTime":"2018-11-29T17:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T05:58:32.000Z","uid":74065,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c89e735ad776dc5b3a5f2e8e5d63ec7af7f19fa5","tid":921660,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.focussy.com/sharing/1811/131879243355704756532_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2Fsharing%2F1811%2F131879243355704756532_L.jpg&h=97f58eec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近在IZ*ONE簽名會上，工作人員在整理禮物箱時，發現一個存有巨額現金的信封！根據在2016年修訂的韓國《金英蘭法》，為了打擊嚴重的貪污，公務人員、媒體等行業人士不得收100萬韓元以上的財務，否則將受到刑事處罰。因此，不少經紀公司會要求粉絲將禮物送到公司過濾，若太昂貴的話，會要求退掉哦！在簽名會上也是如此，IZ*ONE所屬的Off The Record曾強調現金、禮券等物品是禁止贈送給成員們，因此出現這麼巨額的現金信封，公司立馬透過官咖發公告，要求當事人現身領回！<br />\n若在12月7日之後仍未有人聯絡Off The Record公司，該現金將以WIZ*ONE的名義捐贈給慈善機構。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨後，已經有粉絲站出來承認是他送的哦！原來是一名相當有人氣的網路漫畫家「옥쨩」出席IZ*ONE簽名會，而他也透過DC Gallery論壇承認是自己為張元英準備的禮物。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1811/so1318793014692388273882.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1811%2Fso1318793014692388273882.jpg&h=649604ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他透露自己是第一次追星，不晓得藝人們不能收現金，而官咖中也沒有提到此事。因此，<span style=\"color: red;\">當他出席IZ*ONE的簽名會時，準備了張元英的自畫像、一臺iPhone XS Max手機、Airpod耳機、親筆信和一封存有100萬韓元的「零用錢」。</span>「옥쨩」心想著張元英剛出道不久，應該沒那麼快會領到第一筆薪水，希望這筆現金能讓她買點自己喜歡的東西，吃好一點哦！<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.focussy.com/sharingSub/1811/so131879301469550828477.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.focussy.com%2FsharingSub%2F1811%2Fso131879301469550828477.jpg&h=899e927c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只是，工作人員看到手機的時候，就已經立即被拿走了，因為禮物的價格太昂貴啦！不過，由於現金是裝在信封內，工作人員也沒當場打開檢查，所以沒有第一時間被發現。只是，事後經紀公司發公告透露此事，「옥쨩」才晓得送現金是被禁止的舉動呢~ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母你當元英BB係咩阿垃圾韓仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd91cbb9bd641a46b832ff54edbef104d2eb54a","tid":921660,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:47:38.000Z","msg":"當元英係好女仔"},{"pid":"4e0a5feaad2d10d4cdc1a2895689d09d8cbf2eb3","tid":921660,"uid":17266,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:59:06.000Z","msg":"送錢比老細條女緊係唔得啦"},{"pid":"01912382b1f15cd2d669a999ae68f2bfc7c67fc4","tid":921660,"uid":176935,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T18:00:01.000Z","msg":"其實佢好有心<br />\n佢知韓國做idol 多數都唔會被善待<br />\n可能要等3-4 年先有人工<br />\n佢真心錫元英<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  值得加許"},{"pid":"bb414ff582cec472b8aa6c799001051a5aebf12d","tid":921660,"uid":80814,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T18:41:24.000Z","msg":"咁班staff拎走部iphone xs，係想自己獨吞咗，定還返畀個fans架? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲濕鳩公司成日擅自攞咗fans送畀idol嘅貴禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aacfae58e80bfadcd0a2bbc18ca2d4944f8d9e8","tid":921660,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T18:44:30.000Z","msg"